OL,3,CScotland's budget wasn't dramatic, but
OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Scotland Reporter
OL,7,FVanessa Taaffe and Scotland Producer
OL,8,FStephanie Docherty
OL,10,FThis was certainly a budget made up of
OL,11,Fsmall measures to try and ease the
OL,12,Fsqueeze for Scottish families.
OL,14,FThere wasn't exactly a standout,
OL,15,Fdramatic policy moment from the
OL,16,Ffinance secretary on Tuesday
OL,17,Fafternoon, but Shona Robison said it
OL,18,Fwould be a budget for families,
OL,19,Foffering up extra cash for the those
OL,20,Fstruggling the most.
