OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FThe Scottish child payment, a Scottish
OL,7,Fgovernment benefit for low-income
OL,8,Ffamilies with children under 16, is
OL,9,Fgoing from just over #27 a week to #40
OL,10,Fa week for babies.
