OL,3,CScotland's budget wasn't dramatic, but
OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FWhile this is a headline-grabbing
OL,7,Fpolicy, experts from the Fraser of
OL,8,FAllander Institute have calculated
OL,9,Fthat only around 12,000 children are
OL,10,Flikely to be eligible for this,
OL,11,Fmeaning it's not an expensive
OL,12,Fcommitment from the Scottish
OL,13,Fgovernment.
