OL,3,CScotland's budget wasn't dramatic, but
OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FAlso on offer for families is the
OL,7,Fexpansion of breakfast clubs and a
OL,8,Fcommitment to more free sporting
OL,9,Fopportunities for children. Robison
OL,10,Flinked this to Scotland's 'Summer of
OL,11,FSport', with Glasgow hosting the
OL,12,FCommonwealth Games and Scotland's men
OL,13,Fqualifying for the football World Cup.
OL,15,FElsewhere, there are some new taxes
OL,16,Faimed at the wealthy. A so-called
OL,17,F"mansion tax" for properties over #1
OL,18,Fmillion is to be introduced along with
OL,19,Fa new tax on those who travel by
OL,20,Fprivate jet.
