OL,3,CScotland's budget wasn't dramatic, but
OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FStaying with taxes, there have been
OL,7,Fsome changes to the thresholds for the
OL,8,Ftwo lowest income tax bands, resulting
OL,9,Fin those earning less than #30,000 a
OL,10,Fyear paying slightly less tax than in
OL,11,Fthe rest of the UK.
OL,13,FAnd finally, the finance secretary
OL,14,Fannounced more record spending on the
OL,15,FNHS.
OL,17,FMoney has been freed up to open new
OL,18,Fwalk-in high street GP clinics, as
OL,19,Fwell as extra cash for frontline
OL,20,Fhealth and social care services.
