OL,3,CScotland's budget wasn't dramatic, but
OL,4,Csmall measures could benefit families
OL,6,FThe opposition parties have pointed
OL,7,Fout this is the nineteenth SNP budget,
OL,8,Fclaiming it's just more of the same
OL,9,Fand will not deliver the change
OL,10,FScotland needs.
OL,12,FWith a Holyrood election looming, some
OL,13,Fof these policies may not even come to
OL,14,Fpass if there's a new government in
OL,15,FMay.
